OL,3,CWatchdog warns of 'national security
OL,4,Cthreat' from drone drug drops to jails
OL,6,FDrones dropping drugs and weapons to
OL,7,Fdangerous prisoners being held in high-
OL,8,Fsecurity jails are a "threat to
OL,9,Fnational security", a watchdog has
OL,10,Fwarned.
OL,12,FChief Inspector of Prisons Charlie
OL,13,FTaylor accused the police and
OL,14,Fgovernment of giving up control of the
OL,15,Fairspace above HMP Manchester and HMP
OL,16,FLong Lartin in Worcestershire, as he
OL,17,Fcalled on them and the security
OL,18,Fservices to "urgently confront"
OL,19,Factivity from criminal gangs behind
OL,20,Fthe supply.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@RO]zD@MOUzD@_O]
