OL,3,CWatchdog warns of 'national security
OL,4,Cthreat' from drone drug drops to jails
OL,6,FPublishing the findings of inspections
OL,7,Fat the two prisons on Tuesday, 14
OL,8,FJanuary, he raised serious concerns
OL,9,Fover safety and basic security,
OL,10,Fdescribing the jails as having
OL,11,F"thriving" drug economies with nets
OL,12,Fand CCTV being allowed to fall into
OL,13,F"disrepair".
OL,15,FThe scale of the problem at HMP
OL,16,FManchester, previously known as
OL,17,FStrangeways, included inmates burning
OL,18,Fholes in windows to receive drone
OL,19,Fdeliveries and prompted Mr Taylor to
OL,20,Ftell the Justice Secretary to put the
OL,21,Fprison into emergency measures in 2024.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@JO]uD@AOU
