OL,3,CWatchdog warns of 'national security
OL,4,Cthreat' from drone drug drops to jails
OL,6,FAnd a report from Independent
OL,7,FMonitoring Boards (IMB) ` made up of
OL,8,Fvolunteers tasked by ministers with
OL,9,Fscrutinising conditions in custody `
OL,10,Finto "crumbling" jails in England and
OL,11,FWales said delays in fixing broken
OL,12,Fprison windows was making it easier
OL,13,Ffor drones to be used to deliver drugs
OL,14,Fand weapons.
OL,16,FIn December, MPs heard contraband was
OL,17,Fbeing taken into HMP Parc in South
OL,18,FWales in "children's nappies", while
OL,19,Fthere were "industrial specification
OL,20,Fdrone drops being organised by
OL,21,Forganised crime gangs".
OL,26,@rD@FOUrD@PO]zD@JOUzD@]O]{D@LOU}D@VO]
