OL,3,CWatchdog warns of 'national security
OL,4,Cthreat' from drone drug drops to jails
OL,6,FAndrea Coomber KC (Hon.), Chief
OL,7,FExecutive of the Howard League for
OL,8,FPenal Reform, said: "These appalling
OL,9,Finspection reports are a warning that
OL,10,Fproblems in prisons spill out into the
OL,11,Ftowns and cities around them.
OL,13,FA system that has been asked to do too
OL,14,Fmuch, with too little, for too long is
OL,15,Fnow so compromised as to become a
OL,16,Fthreat to national security.
OL,26,@pD@UOU
