OL,4,Cthreat' from drone drug drops to jails
OL,6,FAndrea Coomber from the Howard League
OL,7,Ffor Penal Reform
OL,9,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,10,Fsaid: "This Government inherited
OL,11,Fprisons in crisis - overcrowded, with
OL,12,Fdrugs and violence rife.
OL,14,F"We are gripping the situation by
OL,15,Finvesting in prison maintenance and
OL,16,Fsecurity, working with the police and
OL,17,Fothers to tackle serious organised
OL,18,Fcrime, and building more prison places
OL,19,Fto lock up dangerous criminals."
OL,26,@rD@GOUvD@AOU{D@`O]
